{"tid":1874733,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"好快就立法會選舉，你地係唔係仲要救班藍絲投少數派？","createTime":"2020-02-11T11:08:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-12T02:27:20.000Z","uid":107590,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"31181c8bb1009145f2191f29a9c6df16877dc0dc","tid":1874733,"uid":107590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T11:08:01.000Z","msg":"今次係大好機會重創對家，等人地少得一個得一個<br />\n點解仲要咁大愛幫佢地要老野先比派口罩？<br />\n<br />\n中國人特質係，當完左呢件事就會覺得唔關佢事，唔會反省反思政府同自已，甚至會話返你地誇張<br />\n點解呀？因為佢冇事呀！ <br />\n佢地覺得冇事係因為個病誇張左，唔撚係你派口罩比佢呀！<br />\n<br />\n而且，都半年啦，今時今日仲藍緊既個腦跟本冇得救<br />\n你救佢個肉身黎只會係立選度幫對手補血<br />\n<br />\n抗爭未完架，你地點對得住啲手足呀！"},{"pid":"b617ba5336e3e12fdd4f1a5907142e011d9a7ea4","tid":1874733,"uid":192824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T11:12:35.000Z","msg":"從來係自保"},{"pid":"a0bf362ce73add064a30b65eea6e823629f3680b","tid":1874733,"uid":107590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T11:17:36.000Z","msg":"今次立法會輸左，你地對唔對得住手足？"},{"pid":"c2b29f3e4fa166570938d7ca8f40a6c846542df7","tid":1874733,"uid":107590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b617ba5336e3e12fdd4f1a5907142e011d9a7ea4","tid":1874733,"uid":192824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T11:12:35.000Z","msg":"從來係自保"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T11:35:42.000Z","msg":"班大愛撚係咩心態？<br />\n想感化佢地？"},{"pid":"a59014eeaaf8d613c6af2ce6d56367fb125b1d76","tid":1874733,"uid":100155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T14:15:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JOowZpL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJOowZpL.png&h=8c2863cd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n特區政府（又稱港共傀儡政權）由組成到管治都毫無正當性。 港人應學委內瑞拉，自組港人政府，再予美國及西方承認<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1875043\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1875043</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"8e853849cd7ec4f295543db8244a300b0a2665e3","tid":1874733,"uid":107590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedB